Fu Zi is Kong Fu Zi. He is known in Chinese era as A Great Philosopher that becomes worshipped Deity of Taoism. "Kong" is his Surname. Don't misunderstood it for WuKong or KingKong, this had nothing to do with them. Kong Fu Zi is a Chinese and original name of Confucius. Adam Cheng himself prior to the show said that he will be portraying Confucius on the show. So don't tell me, I don't have reliable sources
